{"type":"message","id":"139e7df3","parentId":"9e5a785c","timestamp":"2026-06-21T03:10:43.731Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-06-21 11:10:43 GMT+8] Exec failed (tender-t, code 1) :: 登录检查失败: HTTPConnectionPool(host='localhost', port=18060): Read timed out. (read timeout=15) 搜索 旅游 出错: Expecting value: line 1 column 1 (char 0) 搜索 旅行 出错: HTTPConnectionPool(host='…\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/linkang/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Sunday, June 21st, 2026 — 11:10 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-06-21 03:10 UTC"}],"timestamp":1782011443729}}
{"type":"message","id":"2d1e2c39","parentId":"139e7df3","timestamp":"2026-06-21T03:10:50.751Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The system is reporting that an exec failed with a timeout error related to the 小红书 MCP (port 18060). The error message shows \"登录检查失败: HTTPConnectionPool(host='localhost', port=18060): Read timed out\" - this means the 小红书 MCP service timed out during a login check.\n\nLet me check the HEARTBEAT.md file to see if there's anything specific I need to do."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_110a1dce428241e5b6dc575a","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/linkang/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782011443730}}
{"type":"message","id":"42a68eb8","parentId":"2d1e2c39","timestamp":"2026-06-21T03:10:50.770Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_110a1dce428241e5b6dc575a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat\n\n每次心跳唤醒时，按以下逻辑判断是否需要主动联系用户。\n\n## 时间感知\n\n根据当前时间（Asia/Shanghai）判断所处时段：\n- **工作日 9:30-11:30** — 上午工作时段\n- **工作日 13:30-18:00** — 下午工作时段\n- **工作日 11:30-13:30** — 午休，不打扰\n- **18:00 之后** — 下班时间，不打扰\n- **周末** — 休息日，不打扰\n\n## 检查规则\n\n仅在工作时段执行以下检查，其他时间直接回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n### 1. 喝水提醒（10:30 / 14:30 / 16:30 附近）\n简短提醒喝水，不超过一句话。每次都要提醒，不要因为之前提醒过就跳过。\n\n### 2. 久坐提醒（连续工作超过 2 小时的时间点）\n建议站起来活动一下，不要说教。每次都要提醒。\n\n### 3. 周五 17:00 附近\n提醒写周报。每次都要提醒直到用户确认已写。\n\n## 原则\n\n- 不打扰优先：有疑问时选择沉默，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n- 重复提醒：喝水、久坐、周报这类事项每次心跳都可以提醒，不要怕重复\n- 简短：提醒不超过 2 行\n- 可以催进度：工作时段内可以主动问用户在做什么、进展如何，适当推一把\n- 午休（11:30-13:30）和下班后（18:00+）绝对不打扰\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1782011450769}}
{"type":"message","id":"e6bf3efb","parentId":"42a68eb8","timestamp":"2026-06-21T03:10:56.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It's 11:10 on Sunday, June 21st, 2026. This is weekend/休息日, so I should not打扰 and just reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\n\nAlso there was an error in the system message about 小红书 MCP connection failing (HTTPConnectionPool timeout). This seems to be a background task that failed, but it's not something I need to proactively inform the user about right now since they're in rest mode.\n\nJust reply HEARTBE"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782011450771}}
